      <body>
         <div type="retro">
             <div type="message">
                        <opener xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">
                                <dateline>
                                        <lb n="1"/>
                                        <s>
                                                <placeName ref="list.xml#MO">Modena</placeName>, li 
                                                <date when="1917-11-29">29/11-17</date>
                                        </s>
                                </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="postcard-body">
                                <p>
                                        <lb n="2"/>
                                        Oliva mia,
                                        <lb n="3"/>
                                        Non puoi credere quanto mi sia diventato
                                        <lb n="4"/>
                                        odioso questo materialismo fugato, <choice>
                                                                                <orig>asfillante</orig>
                                                                                <reg resp="list.xml#LR" cert="high">assillante</reg>
                                                                          </choice>, avido;
                                        <lb n="5"/>
                                        che vivo in una <choice>
                                                                <orig>incufante</orig>
                                                                <reg resp="list.xml#LR" cert="high">incusante</reg>
                                                        </choice> monotonia di fredda
                                        <lb n="6"/>
                                        solitudine. Non una favola buona, un consiglio
                                        <lb n="7"/>
                                        un sorriso, uno sguardo affettuoso, nulla che si
                                        <lb n="8"/>
                                        allontani, si elevi dall'insulsa obbrobriosa
                                        <lb n="9"/>
                                        sterile norma delle cose inanimate che ti circonda
                                        <lb n="10"/>
                                        no, nulla per questa mia anima sitibonda
                                        <lb n="11"/>
                                        d'affetto, d'amore, di pace.
                                </p>
                        </div>
                        <closer xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">
                                <lb n="12"/>
                                tuo <signed>
                                        <persName>
                                                <forename ref="list.xml#GC">Giovannino</forename>
                                        </persName>
                                </signed>
                        </closer>
